These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
Sport: soccer, cycling, ice-hockey, sailing
Transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. Sport:sailing is on the left of Sport:soccer##1
2. Sport:soccer is on the right of Sport:sailing##1
3. Transport:car is on the far left or far right##3
4. Sport:ice-hockey is on the right of Transport:motorbike##1
5. Transport:roller is between Transport:car and Transport:motorbike##2
6. Sport:sailing == Transport:bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | sailing | soccer     | ice-hockey | cycling |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
Music-Genre: gospel, hip-hop, rock, techno
Pet: rabbit, pony, frog, turtle
1. Music-Genre:hip-hop is on the left of Pet:pony##1
2. Pet:turtle is on the far left or far right##3
3. Music-Genre:techno is on the left of Pet:turtle##1
4. Pet:turtle is on the right of Pet:pony##1
5. Music-Genre:rock is on the far right##1
6. Pet:rabbit is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop    | techno     | rock  |
| Pet     | rabbit    | frog | pony | turtle |

