2. Hobby:fishing is between Hobby:board-games and Transport:roller##2
3. Hobby:fishing is on the left or right of Hobby:dancing##3
4. Transport:roller is on the left or right of Transport:quad-bike##3
5. Hobby:board-games is on the right of Hobby:collecting##1
6. Transport:skateboard is on the right of Transport:car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | board-games | fishing | dancing  |
| Transport   | car  | skateboard   | quad-bike  | roller |

